## 八、CSS Override 参考（补充到 el-overrides.css）

```css
/* ===== Input Trigger ===== */
.el-input__wrapper {
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);     /* 4px */
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #dedfe3 inset;
}

.el-input__wrapper:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--pcv-brand) inset;
}

.el-input__wrapper.is-focus {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--pcv-brand) inset;
}

.el-input.is-disabled .el-input__wrapper {
  background-color: #f4f5f6;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #dedfe3 inset;
}

/* Small size */
.el-input--small .el-input__wrapper {
  height: 32px;
}

/* Placeholder */
.el-input__inner::placeholder {
  color: #b2b2b8;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Value text */
.el-input__inner {
  color: #66666c;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 20px;
}

/* Textarea */
.el-textarea__inner {
  padding: 8px 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid #dedfe3;
  color: #66666c;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 20px;
}

.el-textarea__inner:hover {
  border-color: var(--pcv-brand);
}

.el-textarea__inner:focus {
  border-color: var(--pcv-brand);
  outline: none;
}

/* ===== Form Item Error (失败状态提示文字) ===== */
.el-form-item__error {
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 18px;
  color: #ea5455;
  padding-left: 0;
  padding-top: 4px;
}

/* ===== Success / Warning State (自定义 class) ===== */
.el-input.is-success .el-input__wrapper {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #28c76f inset;
}

.el-input.is-warning .el-input__wrapper {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #ff9f43 inset;
}

/* Success / Warning hint text */
.input-hint--success { color: #28c76f; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; padding-left: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
.input-hint--warning { color: #ff9f43; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; padding-left: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
.input-hint--error   { color: #ea5455; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; padding-left: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }

/* ===== Search Box Style 2 (圆角 6px) ===== */
.pcv-search-input .el-input__wrapper {
  border-radius: 6px;
}
```

